@NODE pp "History/Plans"
@{BG SHINE}
    MagicBar history
@{BG BACK}
v1.0.           - Originally named `WorkBar', however due
                  to lots of bugs this was only available as
                  a BETA version. Never released.

v1.1            + All known major bugs fixed
                + Code more optimized
                + Renamed to MagicBar
                - No colour remapping :(

v1.2            * First release to the public
                + Bitmap remapping
                + Autohide added
                + GlowIcon gadget set added
@{BG SHINE}
    Future plans
@{BG BACK}
* Transparent gadgets
* Smoooooooth autohide function
* New-NewIcon gadget set :)
* Config editor program :))
* Lower and Upper positions (Not just left and right)

